{
  "title": "Xenial Uruguayan Kidney Beans Casserole",
  "description": "Earthy and festive casserole of kidney beans glazed with tomato puree and smoked paprika, finished with a glossy sheen. Kosher-friendly and perfect for a celebratory dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
  "diet": [
